GOVERNMENT OF INDIA (BHARAT SARKAR)
CABINET SECRETARIAT (MANTRIMANDAL SACHIVALAYA)
New Delhi, the 29th June, 2002
8 Asadha, 1924 (S)
The undersigned is directed to state that with effect from the 29th
June, 2002 Shri L.K. Advani will be designated as Deputy Prime Minister.
He will continue to hold the charge of the Ministry of Home Affairs.
(P. Gopalakrishnan)
